headline: US beer sales slump on consumer strain hits Constellation and Molson Coors
summary: Investing.com -- Barclays warned that weak beer demand and economic strain will weigh on volumes and investor sentiment on the U.S. beer sector for some time as it downgraded Constellation Brands and Molson Coors.
